scene.message:
Yukino: The Night Queen called{nl}
this ice-encased school the{nl}
"Ice Castle," didn't she.{waitkey}{clearbox}It's a castle, all right.{nl}
Storming up it is a real{nl}
chore.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I'm thinking of working{nl}
a labyrinth into my home's{nl}
security, as well.{waitkey}What do you think?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Why is this place so{nl}
huge!!{waitkey}Is there really an end to{nl}
it...{waitkey}{ret}
